### Gold Price API Tests

@baseUrl = https://pcaview.abc
# @baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### 1. Get Latest Gold Price
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/latest
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get Gold Price History - Default (1 month, pure gold, domestic)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get Gold Price History - 7 days, pure gold, domestic
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=7d&type=pure&market=domestic
Accept: application/json

### 4. Get Gold Price History - 1 month, 18k gold, domestic
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=1m&type=18k&market=domestic
Accept: application/json

### 5. Get Gold Price History - 3 months, 14k gold, domestic
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=3m&type=14k&market=domestic
Accept: application/json

### 6. Get Gold Price History - 6 months, white gold (platinum), domestic
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=6m&type=white&market=domestic
Accept: application/json

### 7. Get Gold Price History - 1 year, silver, domestic
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=1y&type=silver&market=domestic
Accept: application/json

### 8. Get Gold Price History - All time, pure gold, domestic
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=all&type=pure&market=domestic
Accept: application/json

### 9. Get International Gold Price History - 1 month, gold
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=1m&type=gold&market=international
Accept: application/json

### 10. Get International Silver Price History - 1 month
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=1m&type=silver&market=international
Accept: application/json

### 11. Get International Platinum Price History - 1 month
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=1m&type=platinum&market=international
Accept: application/json

### 12. Get International Palladium Price History - 1 month
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=1m&type=palladium&market=international
Accept: application/json

### 13. Get Statistics - Default (1 month, pure gold)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/statistics
Accept: application/json

### 14. Get Statistics - 7 days, silver
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/statistics?period=7d&type=silver
Accept: application/json

### 15. Get Statistics - 1 year, 18k gold
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/statistics?period=1y&type=18k
Accept: application/json

### Test Silver vs Gold (should return different data)
### 16. Gold data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=1m&type=pure&market=domestic
Accept: application/json

### 17. Silver data (should be different from gold)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=1m&type=silver&market=domestic
Accept: application/json

### Invalid requests (should return errors)
### 18. Invalid period
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=invalid&type=pure&market=domestic
Accept: application/json

### 19. Invalid type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=1m&type=invalid&market=domestic
Accept: application/json

### 20. Invalid market
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gold/history?period=1m&type=pure&market=invalid
Accept: application/json
